    "description": "<strong>Triversal</strong> is a satisfying puzzle game that offers the perfect balance of chill and challenge. <br>Use spatial logic to suspend a sun over a black hole by connecting it to stretchy tethers.<br><br>This <strong>V2 Steam Edition</strong> has been rebalanced and expanded with new modes, puzzle packs and ways to play.<br><br><strong>A Snack for your Brain:</strong> A perfect palette cleanser between intense tasks, whether you have a couple minutes or a couple hours to unwind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481000/extras/b163ba078cc3e59773d17cf9f1f4b531.poster.avif?t=1715800010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481000/extras/b163ba078cc3e59773d17cf9f1f4b531.webm?t=1715800010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481000/extras/b163ba078cc3e59773d17cf9f1f4b531.mp4?t=1715800010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Pick Up and Play:</strong> Triversal is easy to learn and satisfying to master; simply add and remove elastic tethers to pull the light sun so it lines up with the black hole. Play with mouse, keyboard or a controller.  It’s as easy as 1-2-3.<br><br><strong>A Perfect Balance of Chill and Challenge:</strong> Triversal offers a gentle learning curve and a range of puzzles and modes to suit your mood.<br><br>     <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Daily Puzzle:</strong>  Rack up perfect streaks, collect coins and compete for a high score on a new challenge daily.  </li></ul>     <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Endurance:</strong>  Complete level after level of progressively more difficult procedurally generated puzzles where each move costs a coin. Try to beat your high score before you run out of coins altogether in Standard, Pro or Classic Endurance.</li></ul>     <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Sandbox:</strong>  Dial in your level of challenge to improve your strategy &amp; skills or play through endless puzzles with no risk, no scores and no stress.</li></ul>     <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Puzzle Packs:</strong>  Hundreds of levels in dozens of packs to work through at your own pace. </li></ul><br><strong>Streamer Assist:</strong> Collaborate with your streaming audience with the Streamer Assist feature, an optional overlay that adds numbered labels to your puzzles, allowing viewers to play along in chat by suggesting solutions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481000/extras/3907919794031a51c24b2763896666b2.poster.avif?t=1715800010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481000/extras/3907919794031a51c24b2763896666b2.webm?t=1715800010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481000/extras/3907919794031a51c24b2763896666b2.mp4?t=1715800010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
